# Omelette Frontend Standards

- React 18 + TypeScript strict mode
- Use `@/` path alias for imports (configured in tsconfig and vite)
- TailwindCSS v4 for styling — use utility classes, avoid CSS modules
- Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for conditional class merging
- TanStack Query for all API data fetching
- Zustand for client-side state management
- API calls through `@/lib/api.ts` axios instance
- Types in `@/types/index.ts` must match backend Pydantic schemas
- Functional components only, no class components
- Vite dev server on port 3000, proxies `/api` to backend port 8000
